summary: The number 4,294,967,295 is a whole number equal to 232 − 1. It is a perfect totient number, meaning it is equal to the sum of its iterated totients.[1][2] It follows 4,294,967,294 and precedes 4,294,967,296. It has a factorization of 3 ⋅ 5 ⋅ 17 ⋅ 257 ⋅ 65537 {\displaystyle 3\cdot 5\cdot 17\cdot 257\cdot 65537} .
